{
  "id": "core-principles",
  "title": "Core Principles",
  "blocks": [
    { "type": "h1", "text": "What is Drumee?" },

    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Drumee is a secure cloud workspace that brings  **files, conversations, notes, and contacts** together in one place."
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Instead of switching between file storage, chat tools, and note apps, Drumee organizes everything around **folders and people**, with privacy and access control built in by default."
    },

    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Drumee is designed for:"
    },

    {
      "type": "ul",
      "items": [
        "Individuals who want a private cloud space",
        "Teams collaborating on shared files",
        "Users who need to share content securely with external people"
      ]
    },

    { "type": "h1", "text": "How Drumee Works (Core Principles)" },

    { "type": "h2", "text": "1. Workspace" },

    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Your workspace is your **personal cloud environment**. Everything you do in Drumee happens inside this workspace."
    },

    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Inside a workspace, you can:"
    },

    {
      "type": "ul",
      "items": [
        "Create folders",
        "Upload files",
        "Chat with collaborators",
        "Write notes",
        "Manage contacts and settings"
      ]
    },

    { "type": "h2", "text": "2. Folders Are the Center of Everything" },

    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "In Drumee, folders are more than storage."
    },
    {
      "type": "ul",
      "items": [
        "Files",
        "Messages (chat)",
        "Shared access with specific people"
      ]
    },

    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Each folder has its **own privacy rules**."
    },

    { "type": "h1", "text": "Folder Types" },

    {
      "type": "h3",
      "text": "Private Folder"
    },
    {
      "type": "ul",
      "items": [
        "Only visible to you",
        "No one else can access it",
        "Best for personal documents, drafts, or sensitive files"
      ]
    },

    { "type": "h3", "text": "External Folder" },

    {
      "type": "ul",
      "items": [
        "Can be shared with other users",
        "Used for collaboration",
        "Includes both files and chat messages"
      ]
    },

    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "When you create a folder, you choose its type based on how you want to use it."
    },

    { "type": "h1", "text": " Files & Storage" },

    { "type": "h3", "text": "Uploading Files" },

    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "You can upload files directly into any folder you own or have access to."
    },

    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Supported use cases include:"
    },

    {
      "type": "ul",
      "items": ["Documents", "Images", "Videos", "Notes"]
    },

    { "type": "h3", "text": "Storage Overview" },

    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "In **Settings → Storage**, you can:"
    },

    {
      "type": "ul",
      "items": [
        "See how much storage you’ve used",
        "SView usage by file type (video, image, note, all files)",
        "Upgrade your plan if needed"
      ]
    },

    { "type": "h1", "text": "Chat & Communication" },

    { "type": "h3", "text": "Folder-Based Chat" },

    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Every shared folder includes a chat panel."
    },

    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "This means:"
    },
    {
      "type": "ul",
      "items": [
        "Conversations stay tied to files",
        "No need to search for context",
        "Messages belong to the work, not a separate app"
      ]
    },

    { "type": "h3", "text": "Sending Messages" },

    {
      "type": "ul",
      "items": [
        "Messages appear with timestamps",
        "Delivery and read status are shown",
        "Chats update in real time"
      ]
    },

    { "type": "h1", "text": "Contacts" },

    { "type": "h3", "text": "What Are Contacts?" },

    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Contacts are the people you interact with in Drumee."
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "You can:"
    },

    {
      "type": "ul",
      "items": [
        "Add contacts",
        "Invite new users",
        "Organize contacts using tags"
      ]
    },

    { "type": "h3", "text": "Managing Invitations" },

    {
      "type": "ul",
      "items": [
        "**Pending invitations** show users who haven’t joined yet",
        "**Archived contacts** are hidden but not deleted"
      ]
    },

    { "type": "h1", "text": "Notes" },

    { "type": "h3", "text": "Creating Notes" },

    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Notes are lightweight documents used for:"
    },

    {
      "type": "ul",
      "items": ["Personal reminders", "Meeting notes", "Quick ideas"]
    },

    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Each note includes:"
    },

    {
      "type": "ul",
      "items": [
        "PA creation timestamp",
        "Editable content",
        "Manual save option"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Notes are stored securely inside your workspace."
    },

    { "type": "h1", "text": "Activity & Notifications" },

    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "The **Activity panel** shows:"
    },

    {
      "type": "ul",
      "items": ["Recent actions", "Updates related to files and messages"]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "You can:"
    },
    {
      "type": "ul",
      "items": [
        "Review what happened while you were away",
        "Mark all notifications as read"
      ]
    },

    { "type": "h1", "text": "Customizing Your Workspace" },

    { "type": "h3", "text": "Background & Theme" },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "You can personalize how Drumee looks:"
    },

    {
      "type": "ul",
      "items": [
        "Choose a built-in background",
        "Upload your own image (up to 10 MB)",
        "Select a color theme"
      ]
    },

    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Customization only affects your own workspace view."
    },

    { "type": "h1", "text": "Account Settings" },

    { "type": "h3", "text": "Profile" },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "In **Settings → Profile**, you can:"
    },

    {
      "type": "ul",
      "items": [
        "Update your name",
        "Change your avatar",
        "Manage your email and country"
      ]
    },

    { "type": "h3", "text": "Security" },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "In **Settings → Security**, you can:"
    },

    {
      "type": "ul",
      "items": [
        "Change your password",
        "Enable multi-factor authentication (MFA)",
        "Log out from the current device"
      ]
    },

    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "MFA adds an extra layer of protection to your account."
    },

    { "type": "h1", "text": "Privacy & Access Control" },

    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Drumee is privacy-first by design."
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Key rules:"
    },

    {
      "type": "ul",
      "items": [
        "Private folders are never shared",
        "External folders are accessible only to invited users",
        "Access is controlled at the folder level",
        "You decide who can see and interact with your content"
      ]
    },

    { "type": "h1", "text": "Typical Use Cases" },

    { "type": "h3", "text": "Personal Workspace" },

    {
      "type": "ul",
      "items": [
        "Private folders for documents",
        "Notes for daily planning",
        "Customized background"
      ]
    },

    { "type": "h3", "text": "Team Collaboration" },

    {
      "type": "ul",
      "items": [
        "External folders for shared projects",
        "Folder-based chat for discussions",
        "Controlled access for each collaborator"
      ]
    },

    { "type": "h3", "text": "External Sharing" },

    {
      "type": "ul",
      "items": [
        "Share files without exposing your entire workspace",
        "Keep conversations and files in one place"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
